generatedPrompts.frontCover: Flat 2D illustration for a greeting card. In a dreamy fantasy art style, an illustrated version of Jordan from the photo is playfully piggybacking an illustrated version of Lao Lao from the photo. They both have joyful, energetic expressions and are laughing. Jordan wears a maroon t-shirt and Lao Lao wears the yellow floral dress from the photo. They are running through a magical, oversized forest at twilight where the flora glows with soft neon light. Fantastical, whimsical creatures like tiny winged foxes and glowing sprites peek out from behind giant, iridescent mushrooms and luminous, swirling ferns. The air is filled with floating, sparkling dust motes and gentle bubbles of light. In the center of the image, the text "Happy Birthday, my love" is written in a beautiful, readable, glowing white handwritten cursive script. The overall composition is dynamic and full of movement, with a vibrant, ethereal color palette of deep blues, purples, pinks, and glowing teals.

generatedPrompts.rightInterior:
Flat 2D illustration for the right interior of a greeting card, designed to leave ample space for a handwritten message. In a dreamy fantasy anime style, a minimal decorative border frames the page. The top-left and bottom-right corners feature small, delicate arrangements of glowing, ethereal flora, such as luminous swirling ferns and tiny iridescent mushroom caps. A few sparkling dust motes drift near the corners. The central area is a soft, clean wash of pastel pink and light teal, creating an elegant, open space for text. The visual density is minimal (20% decoration), focusing on the message area while maintaining the magical, enchanting aesthetic.
